title: Growth & Learning
content:
“Mistakes are proof that you are trying.”

“If you learn from failure, you haven’t really failed.”

The expert in anything was once a beginner.

Don't giveup early.
Don't loss your hope. 
Dreams comes trues one day stay focused and clam.
